what they cost, in case you will not abate on the price you have noted them
att Æ24:- ap is morethen their price: the kersies I confess are good butt not
to do any goods pon them for mee, so can not give more then o21:10 att
which prijse in case you please you may send mee the rest, whilst intrim
send yd acquittance with some frusty schipper orother for the goods now sent
& Ill pay itt in silve or goeden spetie, hopeing you will abate some thing
to make mee no looser which wholly referre to yd discretion, & as for the

Sr. my last to you was on the 10: curitt sence the french sury is some what over whilst this-
day I have sent to newport the packett CF.NN.8 of which inclosed you have the invoyce
which Ican not question butt must prove well for they are picht out of all the best
sever had and are made up as V.S. tamp hath his, so I hope itt shall come well
to yd handes whilst all the rest of yd ggood order is ready & will follow p. next post
made up in 2 severall packetts, so that these last, three packetts will bedon up each
un a perticular manner, & then when you recaeve y please to examm each & such way as
you like best shall becontinend, that of N.8. Ilook up on the best because the laces are
coulded as broad againe as them & sent you for the ir. of thes please to give mee
eedett & so remanne
